## How to query

You'd be able to query your books like:

```graphql
{
  allBooks {
    edges {
      node {
        content
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Which would return:

```javascript
{
  allBooks: {
    edges: [
      {
        node: {
          content: 'Gambardella, Matthew'
        }
      },
      {
        node: {
          content: 'XML Developer's Guide
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

